            "title": "港股開市︱初段略彈 恒指回升43點報25804點 澳達復牌炒高1.15倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段略作反彈，恒生指數開市報25804點，升43點或0.17%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5546點，升11點或0.21%；國企指數以9051點開市，升23點或0.26%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股互有升跌，阿里巴巴(09988)今早在港開報153.1元，跌0.33%；騰訊(00700)開報610元，跌0.16%；美團(03690)開報96.8元，升0.94%；京東(09618)開報116.2元，升0.61%；小米(01810)開報40.34元，升0.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩大藍籌國際金融股當中，滙控(00005)開報111.1元，逆市微跌0.09%；友邦(01299)開報79.55元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230704-174447_source-web_美團1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230704-174447_source-web_美團1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">均勝電子(00699)獲調入港股通，該股今早開報18元，升1.12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">萬物雲(02602)擬斥最多5億元人民幣回購H股，該股今早開報20.16元，升1.66%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">澳達控股(09929)獲深圳上市公司姚記科技(002605.SZ)董事長姚朔斌收購控股權，並以同價每股0.11元提全面收購，作價較停牌前收市價有溢價6.36%；該股今早復牌應聲炒上，以0.221元開市，飆1.15%。</p>\n</div>",
